Package: linux-headers-asahi-edge${variant:suffix}
Architecture: arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-asahi-edge
Description: Asahi Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest asahi-edge kernel headers
 available.

